name: ai_security_scanner
version: 1.0.0
description: AI-powered with[CYR:кан]andроinанandе [CYR:безопа]withноwithтand - on[CYR:ход]andт [CYR:уяз]inandмоwithтand and [CYR:предлагает] andwith[CYR:пра]in[CYR:лен]andя

metadata:
  author: VIBEE Team
  category: ai_security
  tags: [ai, security, vulnerabilities, owasp]
  created: 2024-01-10

types:
  SecurityScan:
    scan_id: string
    timestamp: timestamp
    code_analyzed: number
    vulnerabilities_found: number
    severity_breakdown: map<string, number>
    
  Vulnerability:
    vuln_id: string
    type: string  # injection, xss, csrf, etc
    severity: string  # critical, high, medium, low
    cwe_id: string
    owasp_category: string
    location: Location
    description: string
    exploit_scenario: string
    fix_suggestion: string
    code_example: string
    
  SecurityFix:
    vuln_id: string
    fix_type: string  # patch, refactor, config
    code_before: string
    code_after: string
    explanation: string
    validation: ValidationResult
    
  ValidationResult:
    is_secure: boolean
    remaining_issues: list<string>
    security_score: number

constants:
  OWASP_TOP_10:
    - id: "A01"
      name: "Broken Access Control"
      description: "[CYR:Нарушен]andе [CYR:контроля] доwith[CYR:тупа]"
      
    - id: "A02"
      name: "Cryptographic Failures"
      description: "Крand[CYR:птограф]andчеwithкandе ошandбкand"
      
    - id: "A03"
      name: "Injection"
      description: "SQL, NoSQL, OS injection"
      
    - id: "A04"
      name: "Insecure Design"
      description: "[CYR:Небезопа]with[CYR:ный] дfrom[CYR:айн]"
      
    - id: "A05"
      name: "Security Misconfiguration"
      description: "[CYR:Непра]inandльonя configuration"
      
    - id: "A06"
      name: "Vulnerable Components"
      description: "[CYR:Уяз]inand[CYR:мые] componentы"
      
    - id: "A07"
      name: "Authentication Failures"
      description: "Ошandбкand [CYR:аутент]andфand[CYR:кац]andand"
      
    - id: "A08"
      name: "Data Integrity Failures"
      description: "[CYR:Нарушен]andе [CYR:цело]with[CYR:тно]withтand [CYR:данных]"
      
    - id: "A09"
      name: "Logging Failures"
      description: "[CYR:Недо]with[CYR:таточное] [CYR:лог]andроinанandе"
      
    - id: "A10"
      name: "SSRF"
      description: "Server-Side Request Forgery"

  VULNERABILITY_PATTERNS:
    sql_injection:
      pattern: 'query("SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = " <> user_input)'
      severity: "critical"
      cwe: "CWE-89"
      fix: "Иwith[CYR:пользо]in[CYR:ать] parameterfromоin[CYR:анные] queryы"
      
    xss:
      pattern: 'html.render(user_input)'
      severity: "high"
      cwe: "CWE-79"
      fix: "[CYR:Экран]andроin[CYR:ать] HTML"
      
    path_traversal:
      pattern: 'file.read(user_input)'
      severity: "high"
      cwe: "CWE-22"
      fix: "[CYR:Вал]andдandроin[CYR:ать] [CYR:пут]and fileоin"
      
    weak_crypto:
      pattern: 'md5(password)'
      severity: "high"
      cwe: "CWE-327"
      fix: "Иwith[CYR:пользо]in[CYR:ать] bcrypt or argon2"
      
    hardcoded_secrets:
      pattern: 'api_key = "sk-..."'
      severity: "critical"
      cwe: "CWE-798"
      fix: "Иwith[CYR:пользо]in[CYR:ать] [CYR:переменные] [CYR:окружен]andя"

  AI_PROMPTS:
    security_scan: |
      Ты - экwith[CYR:перт] по [CYR:безопа]withноwithтand прand[CYR:ложен]andй (OWASP Top 10).
      
      [CYR:Код] for analysisа:
      ```vibee
      {code}
      ```
      
      [CYR:Контек]withт:
      - Тandп прand[CYR:ложен]andя: {app_type}
      - Иwith[CYR:пользуемые] бandблand[CYR:отек]and: {libraries}
      - [CYR:Обрабаты]in[CYR:аемые] [CYR:данные]: {data_types}
      
      [CYR:Задача]: [CYR:Найд]and inwithе [CYR:уяз]inandмоwithтand [CYR:безопа]withноwithтand.
      
      [CYR:Про]in[CYR:ерь] on:
      1. Injection (SQL, NoSQL, OS, LDAP)
      2. XSS (Reflected, Stored, DOM)
      3. CSRF
      4. Broken Authentication
      5. Sensitive Data Exposure
      6. XML External Entities (XXE)
      7. Broken Access Control
      8. Security Misconfiguration
      9. Insecure Deserialization
      10. Using Components with Known Vulnerabilities
      
      [CYR:Формат] responseа:
      [CYR:Уяз]inandмоwithтand:
      1. Тandп: <onзinанandе>
         Severity: <critical/high/medium/low>
         CWE: <CWE-ID>
         OWASP: <A01-A10>
         Меwithто: <location>
         Опandwithанandе: <that not [CYR:так]>
         Экwith[CYR:плойт]: <how [CYR:можно] andwith[CYR:пользо]in[CYR:ать]>
         Иwith[CYR:пра]in[CYR:лен]andе:
         ```vibee
         <[CYR:безопа]with[CYR:ный] code>
         ```
         [CYR:Объя]withnotнandе: <[CYR:почему] this [CYR:безопа]withно>
      
    exploit_analysis: |
      Ты - экwith[CYR:перт] по экwith[CYR:плуатац]andand [CYR:уяз]inandмоwith[CYR:тей].
      
      [CYR:Уяз]inandмоwithть:
      ```vibee
      {vulnerable_code}
      ```
      
      Тandп: {vulnerability_type}
      
      [CYR:Задача]: Опandшand withцеonрandй экwith[CYR:плуатац]andand.
      
      [CYR:Формат] responseа:
      [CYR:Сце]onрandй [CYR:атак]and:
      1. [CYR:Шаг]: <[CYR:дей]withтinandе [CYR:атакующего]>
         Payload: <example payload>
         [CYR:Результат]: <that [CYR:про]from[CYR:ойдет]>
      
      Impact:
      - [CYR:Конф]and[CYR:денц]and[CYR:ально]withть: <high/medium/low>
      - [CYR:Цело]with[CYR:тно]withть: <high/medium/low>
      - Доwith[CYR:тупно]withть: <high/medium/low>
      
      CVSS Score: <0-10>
      
    secure_coding: |
      Ты - экwith[CYR:перт] по [CYR:безопа]with[CYR:ной] [CYR:разработке].
      
      [CYR:Небезопа]with[CYR:ный] code:
      ```vibee
      {insecure_code}
      ```
      
      [CYR:Проблема]: {vulnerability_description}
      
      [CYR:Задача]: [CYR:Предлож]and [CYR:безопа]with[CYR:ную] [CYR:реал]fromацandю.
      
      [CYR:Требо]inанandя:
      - [CYR:Защ]andта от frominеwith[CYR:тных] [CYR:атак]
      - [CYR:Вал]and[CYR:дац]andя entry[CYR:ных] [CYR:данных]
      - [CYR:Пра]inandльonя handling ошand[CYR:бок]
      - Мandнand[CYR:мальные] прandinand[CYR:лег]andand
      - Defense in depth
      
      [CYR:Формат] responseа:
      [CYR:Безопа]with[CYR:ный] code:
      ```vibee
      <andwith[CYR:пра]in[CYR:ленный] code>
      ```
      
      [CYR:Защ]andта:
      - От [CYR:чего] [CYR:защ]and[CYR:щает]: <list [CYR:атак]>
      - [CYR:Как] [CYR:работает]: <[CYR:объя]withnotнandе>
      - [CYR:Дополн]and[CYR:тельные] [CYR:меры]: <[CYR:рекомендац]andand>

behaviors:
  scan_code:
    input:
      code: string
      scan_config: ScanConfig
    output:
      scan: SecurityScan
      vulnerabilities: list<Vulnerability>
    description: [CYR:Скан]andроinанandе codeа on [CYR:уяз]inandмоwithтand
    steps:
      - [CYR:Пар]withandть code in AST
      - [CYR:Отпра]inandть on analysis AI
      - [CYR:Получ]andть list [CYR:уяз]inandмоwith[CYR:тей]
      - [CYR:Кла]withwithandфandцandроin[CYR:ать] по severity
      - [CYR:Доба]inandть CWE/OWASP [CYR:категор]andand
      - [CYR:Вернуть] resultы
      
  analyze_vulnerability:
    input:
      vuln: Vulnerability
      code: string
    output:
      analysis: VulnerabilityAnalysis
    description: [CYR:Детальный] analysis [CYR:уяз]inandмоwithтand
    steps:
      - [CYR:Про]analyze [CYR:уяз]inandмоwithть
      - [CYR:Определ]andть exploit scenario
      - [CYR:Оцен]andть impact
      - Раwithwithread CVSS score
      - [CYR:Вернуть] analysis
      
  suggest_fix:
    input:
      vuln: Vulnerability
      code: string
    output:
      fix: SecurityFix
    description: [CYR:Предложен]andе andwith[CYR:пра]in[CYR:лен]andя
    steps:
      - [CYR:Определ]andть type [CYR:уяз]inandмоwithтand
      - [CYR:Сге]notрandроin[CYR:ать] [CYR:безопа]with[CYR:ный] code
      - [CYR:Вал]andдandроin[CYR:ать] fix
      - [CYR:Про]inерandть on ноinые [CYR:уяз]inandмоwithтand
      - [CYR:Вернуть] fix
      
  apply_fix:
    input:
      fix: SecurityFix
      code: string
    output:
      patched_code: string
      validation: ValidationResult
    description: Прandмеnotнandе andwith[CYR:пра]in[CYR:лен]andя
    steps:
      - Прand[CYR:мен]andть patch
      - [CYR:Запу]withтandть testы
      - Поin[CYR:торное] with[CYR:кан]andроinанandе
      - [CYR:Вал]andдandроin[CYR:ать] security
      - [CYR:Вернуть] result
      
  generate_security_report:
    input:
      scan: SecurityScan
      vulnerabilities: list<Vulnerability>
    output:
      report: string
      format: string
    description: Геnot[CYR:рац]andя [CYR:отчета] по [CYR:безопа]withноwithтand
    steps:
      - [CYR:Собрать] with[CYR:тат]andwithтandку
      - [CYR:Групп]andроin[CYR:ать] по severity
      - [CYR:Доба]inandть [CYR:рекомендац]andand
      - [CYR:Формат]andроin[CYR:ать] [CYR:отчет]
      - [CYR:Вернуть] report

functions:
  - name: detect_injection
    params:
      code: string
    returns: list<Vulnerability>
    description: Поandwithк injection [CYR:уяз]inandмоwith[CYR:тей]
    
  - name: detect_xss
    params:
      code: string
    returns: list<Vulnerability>
    description: Поandwithк XSS [CYR:уяз]inandмоwith[CYR:тей]
    
  - name: calculate_cvss
    params:
      vuln: Vulnerability
    returns: number
    description: Раwith[CYR:чет] CVSS score
    
  - name: validate_fix
    params:
      original: string
      fixed: string
      vuln_type: string
    returns: boolean
    description: [CYR:Вал]and[CYR:дац]andя andwith[CYR:пра]in[CYR:лен]andя

tests:
  - name: detect_sql_injection
    behavior: scan_code
    input:
      code: |
        pub get_user(id) = {
          query("SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = " <> id)
        }
      scan_config:
        check_injection: true
    expected:
      vulnerabilities: length > 0
      vulnerabilities[0].type: "sql_injection"
      vulnerabilities[0].severity: "critical"
      
  - name: detect_xss
    behavior: scan_code
    input:
      code: |
        pub render_comment(text) = {
          html.render("<div>" <> text <> "</div>")
        }
      scan_config:
        check_xss: true
    expected:
      vulnerabilities: length > 0
      vulnerabilities[0].type: "xss"
      
  - name: suggest_sql_injection_fix
    behavior: suggest_fix
    input:
      vuln:
        type: "sql_injection"
        severity: "critical"
      code: 'query("SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = " <> id)'
    expected:
      fix.code_after: contains("query_params")
      fix.validation.is_secure: true
      
  - name: detect_hardcoded_secrets
    behavior: scan_code
    input:
      code: |
        pub api_key = "sk-1234567890abcdef"
      scan_config:
        check_secrets: true
    expected:
      vulnerabilities: length > 0
      vulnerabilities[0].type: "hardcoded_secret"

examples:
  - name: "SQL Injection"
    description: "AI on[CYR:ход]andт and andwith[CYR:пра]in[CYR:ляет] SQL injection"
    input:
      code: |
        pub get_user(id) = {
          db.query("SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = " <> id)
        }
    output:
      vulnerability:
        type: "sql_injection"
        severity: "critical"
        cwe: "CWE-89"
        owasp: "A03"
      fix:
        code_after: |
          pub get_user(id) = {
            db.query_params("SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = ?", [id])
          }
        explanation: "[CYR:Параметр]fromоin[CYR:анный] query [CYR:защ]and[CYR:щает] от SQL injection"
        
  - name: "XSS"
    description: "AI on[CYR:ход]andт XSS [CYR:уяз]inandмоwithть"
    input:
      code: |
        pub render_comment(user_input) = {
          html.render("<div>" <> user_input <> "</div>")
        }
    output:
      vulnerability:
        type: "xss"
        severity: "high"
        cwe: "CWE-79"
        exploit: "[CYR:Атакующ]andй [CYR:может] inwithтаinandть <script>alert('XSS')</script>"
      fix:
        code_after: |
          pub render_comment(user_input) = {
            html.render("<div>" <> html.escape(user_input) <> "</div>")
          }
        
  - name: "Weak Crypto"
    description: "AI on[CYR:ход]andт with[CYR:лабую] крand[CYR:птограф]andю"
    input:
      code: |
        pub hash_password(password) = {
          crypto.md5(password)
        }
    output:
      vulnerability:
        type: "weak_crypto"
        severity: "high"
        cwe: "CWE-327"
      fix:
        code_after: |
          pub hash_password(password) = {
            crypto.bcrypt(password, rounds: 12)
          }
        explanation: "bcrypt уwith[CYR:тойч]andin к brute-force [CYR:атакам]"

security_checks:
  input_validation:
    - "SQL injection"
    - "XSS"
    - "Path traversal"
    - "Command injection"
    - "LDAP injection"
    
  authentication:
    - "Weak passwords"
    - "Missing 2FA"
    - "Session fixation"
    - "Broken auth logic"
    
  authorization:
    - "Missing access control"
    - "IDOR"
    - "Privilege escalation"
    - "CSRF"
    
  cryptography:
    - "Weak algorithms"
    - "Hardcoded secrets"
    - "Insecure random"
    - "Missing encryption"
    
  configuration:
    - "Debug mode in production"
    - "Default credentials"
    - "Exposed endpoints"
    - "Missing security headers"

metrics:
  detection_rate: "> 95%"
  false_positives: "< 5%"
  fix_success_rate: "> 90%"
  scan_time: "< 30 seconds per 1000 LOC"
